high_descs: Go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the chef's knife between the two loaves of bread.
Move to the end of the counter with the two loaves of bread.
Slice the bread closest to the edge of the counter.
Go across the room to the fridge.
Put the chef's knife in the fridge.
Go back to the end of the counter with the sliced bread.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Take the slice of bread to the fridge.
Cool off the slice of bread in the fridge.
Take the cold bread to the counter to the left of the fridge.
Set the cold bread down on the counter to the right of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Set a cold piece of bread on the counter.

high_descs: go straight and turn left to face the counter top
pick up the knife with the yellow handle
face the loaf of bread closest to you
slice the loaf of bread on the counter top closest to the edge
walk to the refrigerator and face it
open the refrigerator door and place the knife on the bottom shelf
return to the counter top with the bread
pick up a slice of bread
go back to the refrigerator
open the refrigerator door and place the slice of bread to the left of the knife, then open the door after a few seconds and carry the bread out
turn left, and face the counter top to the left of the refrigerator
place the bread slice on the counter top to the right of the wine bottle
anns.task_desc: Cut a slice of bread and cool it in the refrigerator

high_descs: Move to stand at the end of the counter so two loaves of bread are in front of you.
Pick up the sharp knife  with the yellow handle from the counter.
Position yourself centered with the loaf of bread closest to you while carrying the knife.
Use the knife to slice half the loaf of bread on the counter.
Carry the knife to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the knife on the shelf.
Move back to the end of the counter facing the slice loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the middle of the loaf.
Carry the slice of bread to the fridge.
Place the slice of bread on the shelf to the left of the knife, close the door, and then open the door and remove after a couple seconds.
Carry the slice of bread to the counter with the wine bottle.
Place the slice of bread on the counter to the right of the wine bottle.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled slice of bread near a wine bottle on the counter.
